review_comments.body:
The variable @environment is referenced but not declared in this scope. The function fn_util_get_env() returns the environment value, but it's not being called or assigned to @environment variable.
```suggestion

DECLARE @environment NVARCHAR(100);
SET @environment = dbo.fn_util_get_env();
```

